description: This is a generated Java class used to register Flutter plugins with the Android engine. It programmatically adds plugins for shared preferences and SQLite database support to the Flutter engine instance.

classes.name: GeneratedPluginRegistrant
classes.description: A utility class to register Flutter plugins with the Android engine.

methods.name: registerWith
methods.description: Registers the shared preferences plugin and the sqflite plugin with the Flutter engine, handling exceptions and logging errors.
